      "PAK"
    ],
    "note": "FORGE is Ubisoft's AnvilNext engine asset container. Used in Assassin's Creed series (AC3 through Valhalla), Watch Dogs 1/2, Far Cry 4/5/6, Ghost Recon Wildlands/Breakpoint. Each game ships with many large .forge files. The format evolved significantly — tools are game-version specific."
  },
